Oly,

Same thing happened to me with my 71.  It would run fine for 10 or so miles 
then just quit.  Other times it would not start at all.  Drove me nuts for 
months.

I finally replaced the ignition switch,  I might be wrong, but I believe that 
the 71's ignition is a first and only year probably for that reason.

Change that switch!

